title: The Jboy Show - Why the committee got it right with Seth Galina and Jeffrey Lee

description:
Jboy breaks down the initial College Football Playoff rankings while joined by Seth Galina of Pro Football Focus and On3's Jeffrey Lee. Make sure to check us out LIVE on Youtube every day at 3pm EST, plus follow us @thejboyshow on all social media platforms!
